ent-Z14ClothingMaskGP5 = GP-5 gas mask
    .desc = Soviet gas mask designed specifically for civilian use. GP-5 is the most common gas mask in the post-Soviet space, which is not surprising, because GP-5 was produced three times more than the inhabitants of the Soviet Union. Protects against radiation.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ClothingMaskGP5Green = GP-5 Green Gas Mask
    .desc = A green variant of the GP-5 gas mask providing protection from radiation.
    .suffix = Z14
